"title": "5550: speech, negative aspects of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5550: speech, negative aspects of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The sinfulness of fallen human nature can express itself in speech, provoking God's displeasure and causing enmity and division amongst people.</p>\n<h2>Evil speech comes from a corrupt heart</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:33-Matt12:35\">MAT 12:33–12:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:12-Prov2:15\">PRO 2:12–2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:1-Prov24:2\">PRO 24:1–24:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:10-Matt15:11\">MAT 15:10–15:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:14-Mark7:15\">MRK 7:14–7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:43-Luke6:45\">LUK 6:43–6:45</a></p>\n<h2>Evil speech is a feature of a corrupt society</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:12-Mic6:13\">MIC 6:12–6:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:5\">ISA 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:1-Isa59:4\">ISA 59:1–59:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:12-Isa59:15\">ISA 59:12–59:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:1-Jer9:9\">JER 9:1–9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:29-Rom1:32\">ROM 1:29–1:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:1-2Tim3:5\">2TI 3:1–3:5</a></p>\n<h2>Evil speech provokes God's displeasure</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:22\">PRO 12:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:16-Prov6:19\">PRO 6:16–6:19</a></p>\n<h2>Kinds of evil speech</h2>\n<h3>Profaning God's name</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:7\">EXO 20:7</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:11\">DEU 5:11</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:28\">EXO 22:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:12\">LEV 19:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:19-Ps139:20\">PSA 139:19–139:20</a></p>\n<h3>Lies and deceit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:9\">PSA 5:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:3\">PSA 36:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:1-Ps52:4\">PSA 52:1–52:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:4\">PSA 62:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:5\">PRO 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:25\">PRO 14:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:4\">PRO 15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:20\">PRO 17:20</a></p>\n<h3>Foolish boasting</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:4\">PSA 94:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:2-Ps10:6\">PSA 10:2–10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:3-Ps12:4\">PSA 12:3–12:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:12-Isa10:14\">ISA 10:12–10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3-2Thess2:4\">2TH 2:3–2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:13-Jas4:16\">JAS 4:13–4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:17-2Pet2:18\">2PE 2:17–2:18</a></p>\n<h3>Ridicule and insults</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:12\">PRO 11:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:41-1Sam17:44\">1SA 17:41–17:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:23-2Kgs2:24\">2KI 2:23–2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:19\">NEH 2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:7\">PRO 9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:15-Lam2:16\">LAM 2:15–2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:22\">MAT 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:39-Matt27:44\">MAT 27:39–27:44</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:29-Mark15:32\">MRK 15:29–15:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:35-Luke23:39\">LUK 23:35–23:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:28-John9:29\">JHN 9:28–9:29</a></p>\n<h3>Criticism and complaint</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:1-Num12:15\">NUM 12:1–12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:1-Num16:50\">NUM 16:1–16:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:28\">1SA 17:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:13\">PRO 19:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:9\">PRO 21:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:19\">PRO 21:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:24\">PRO 25:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:2-Acts11:3\">ACT 11:2–11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:14-Phil2:15\">PHP 2:14–2:15</a></p>\n<h3>Slander</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:16\">LEV 19:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:1-1Kgs21:14\">1KI 21:1–21:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:18\">PRO 10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:11\">JAS 4:11</a></p>\n<h3>Cursing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:17\">EXO 21:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:5-2Sam16:8\">2SA 16:5–16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:20\">PRO 20:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:9-Jas3:10\">JAS 3:9–3:10</a></p>\n<h3>Gossip</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:28\">PRO 16:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:13\">PRO 11:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:9\">PRO 17:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:19\">PRO 20:19</a></p>\n<h3>Obscenity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:4\">EPH 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:8\">COL 3:8</a></p>\n<h2>Evil speech is silenced</h2>\n<h3>By God's actions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:41-Ps107:42\">PSA 107:41–107:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:11\">PSA 63:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:63\">EZK 16:63</a></p>\n<h3>By believers' blameless lives</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:15\">1PE 2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:7-Titus2:8\">TIT 2:7–2:8</a></p>",
